io.atlasmap.spi

Interface AtlasModule

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseAtlasModule, ConstantModule, JavaModule, JsonModule, PropertyModule, XmlModule

    public interface AtlasModule
    A SPI contract between AtlasMap core and modules. AtlasMap core engine invokes those methods while processing mappings.
